	<body>
		<outline text="July 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="july2021" >
			<outline text="July 23" type="calendarDay" name="23" >
				<outline text="Sebastian Thrun started the Waymo/Google effort. If you are going to take a class about AI you can’t do much better than him. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/udacity/status/1417953092042113031&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 23 Jul 2021 16:54:26 GMT" tweetId="1418615500393762820" urltweet="https://twitter.com/scobleizer/status/1418615500393762820" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="scobleizer" />
				<outline text="It is on &lt;a href=&quot;https://tv.youtube.com/welcome/?utm_servlet=prod&amp;zipcode=07047&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt; in 4K for the first time. https://t.co/pgk1bcUqTa" type="tweet" created="Fri, 23 Jul 2021 16:48:05 GMT" tweetId="1418613902695301121" urltweet="https://twitter.com/scobleizer/status/1418613902695301121" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="scobleizer" />
				<outline text="I mislead the industry. I focused too much on technology and not enough on experience.

Avaer is right but the answer is not hate and division. If we choose that route Facebook wins. Every time.

Focus on experience.

@kanyewest gets this. 

He is your competition today. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/webmixedreality/status/1418611847830310915&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 23 Jul 2021 16:45:45 GMT" tweetId="1418613314284703748" urltweet="https://twitter.com/scobleizer/status/1418613314284703748" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="scobleizer" />
				<outline text="All new things suck. 

It is part of innovation. &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/vikasreddy/status/1418448052315066371&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 23 Jul 2021 16:41:24 GMT" tweetId="1418612222234828801" urltweet="https://twitter.com/scobleizer/status/1418612222234828801" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="scobleizer" />
				<outline text="Yes! &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/dfarmer/status/1418600816261230604&quot;&gt;[link]&lt;/a&gt;" type="tweet" created="Fri, 23 Jul 2021 16:13:02 GMT" tweetId="1418605082447257602" urltweet="https://twitter.com/scobleizer/status/1418605082447257602" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="scobleizer" />
				</outline>
			</outline>
